{"type": "article", "id": 26648, "title": "不同的夏日白色牛仔造型，适合自信的女生", "description": "虽然不愿意承认，但白色的确是对人有挑战性的颜色，尤其是大面积的白。", "date": "2016-05-11T06:52:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3126, "name": "牛仔"}, {"id": 27439, "name": "白色牛仔"}], "category": 19, "author": 399912, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607192306h2RYVp4G3k8mFExw.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">夏天就要来了，穿白色总是不会出错的。尽管有人会担心白色会显得人身材魁梧，不过，白色是真正属于夏天的颜色，它看起来清爽、干净又凉快。</p>\n<p class=\"\">而白色牛仔单品则是青春亮丽的的代名词，差不多其他单品和它放在一起，都自动带有了浓浓的美式时尚感。下面有几种白色单品：</p>\n<h2>1.白色背带裤</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607192259h2rtbwF1EyMRT6kn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071923002n1ATuyRZUdKmrp3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.42571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607192300LWlYRytwrAONe1Xu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">白色牛仔背带裤看起来可能脱离了“大草原上的小老鼠”的草原感，看起来更有都市穿搭的风格。而上衣选择白色的衬衣或者 T 恤和白色背带牛仔放在一起，倒是不会显得上重下轻。另外，白色背带裤不会显得幼齿，也是难能可贵。</p>\n<h2>2.白色牛仔短裤</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607192301wALHW3IXsvKekUOi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">白色牛仔短裤的穿搭似乎是相当随意的，上身搭配衬衣也看得过去，而且如果戴对了配饰，比如手表，会比单宁色的牛仔短裤看上去稍微正式那么一点点（但是穿着上班你还是得再想想）。</p>\n<h2>3.白色牛仔裤+白上衣</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071923010ky26FTfnMBbm3gX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607192302dpSKuqJCFZ2DWgV4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071923024ZXsDTa5ikvApNoL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607192303ctgWC6YVjb8xkLnK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">全身白是一种聪明的搭配方式。下身可以选择白色的牛仔裤，而上身的白色单品则不用拘泥在牛仔品类，可以是 T 恤，蕾丝上衣或者白色衬衣。这种全身白的效果就像是一股在夏天吹起的清风。</p>\n<h2>4.白色牛仔裤+各式上衣</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607192303QOrDlTRs7x6gCGbF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.475\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607192304Wz0vXI7sFqPfJrVw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50140845\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607192304pnYEQ9alyTd813hX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">牛仔裤很百搭，白色牛仔裤更是白搭中的百搭。除了可以和白色上衣放在一起以外，白色牛仔裤也可以和颜色鲜艳的上衣、格子花纹衬衫、条纹衫放在一起。</p>\n<h2>5.白色牛仔连衣裙</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607192305Ah7GqTF6wOm4rEJK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>白色牛仔连衣裙的特点在于采用了工装风而不是淑女风的版型，有腰有袖有领，算不上正式，但穿起来会显得精神十足。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<h2>7.白色牛仔半裙</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607192305aF7XKZ3mle5E8S0V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">牛仔半裙最近不知道为什么又成了流行。它的好处在于相比白色牛仔裤，不会那么显腿粗。而且，和所有牛仔半裙一样，相当青春活力美少女。</p>\n<h2>8.白色牛仔裤变成 Legging </h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607192306cEP5FbipXaVlCYsy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">另外，把白色 Skinny 当成 Legging 来穿也是一种聪明的办法。只要上衣足够潮，可以是同色系的针织单品，也有可能改良版的中式旗袍上衣也不错。不过重点是，上衣得开叉，露出部分白色 Legging 。</p>\n<p class=\"\">题图和文内图来自：<a href=\"http://stylecaster.com/what-to-wear-with-white-jeans-this-summer/slideshow/20\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">stylecaster</a>、<a href=\"http://stylecaster.com/what-to-wear-with-white-jeans-this-summer/slideshow/20\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">stylecaster</a>、<a href=\"http://www.glamour.com/story/casual-outfit-fall-white-jeans-transition\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">glamour</a>、<a href=\"http://www.vogue.co.uk/fashion/trends/2015-spring-summer/white-denim\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">vogue</a>、<a href=\"http://www.styledomaine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/white-denim.jpg\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">styledomaine</a>、<a href=\"http://www.memorandum.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/current-elliott-white-denim-jean-shirt-dress-san-francisco-fashion-style-blog-blogger-mary-orton-memorandum4.jpg\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">memorandum</a>、<a href=\"http://www.vogue.co.uk/fashion/trends/2015-spring-summer/white-denim\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">vogue</a><br></p>\n\n\n"}